GitOps CI/CD Pipeline Using GitHub Actions and ArgoCD

Overview of Objectives:

Set up a Continuous Integration (CI) workflow using GitHub Actions to perform testing, security scanning, and Docker image publishing.
Establish a GitOps-driven Continuous Deployment (CD) process with ArgoCD to enable automated syncing and application deployment.
Securely manage sensitive data by leveraging GitHub Secrets for credential handling.
Achieve seamless, zero-downtime deployments through ArgoCDâ€™s auto-sync and self-healing capabilities.
